{"tid":1242282,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解戴眼鏡就比人覺得係毒撚","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:27:45.000Z","uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f86b14e59796a96edacdf4f293b4b66de816b2c","tid":1242282,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"已經唔係粗黑框果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859d3e69a135a58156f9e9d9751aa4de41c6878d","tid":1242282,"uid":149357,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"其實有無唸過人地覺得你係毒撚唔係因為你戴眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36d0644199abda1da657327b2d09b27ccab0984","tid":1242282,"uid":123020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859d3e69a135a58156f9e9d9751aa4de41c6878d","tid":1242282,"uid":149357,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"其實有無唸過人地覺得你係毒撚唔係因為你戴眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fff69b04ad691abea28c0e82928ba9f90e548cf","tid":1242282,"uid":257422,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a5f52717340ce1eab17d2faf1b81fe093a68f","tid":1242282,"uid":61018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"你睇吓李局長就知<br />\n毒撚聲<br />\n毒撚回答"},{"pid":"46f4e5e2336418bb683e12597504b97bbd3863af","tid":1242282,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"你唱得好聽咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9d8b81508a87d014e9f187a8a560a9fce312bf","tid":1242282,"uid":223084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"859d3e69a135a58156f9e9d9751aa4de41c6878d","tid":1242282,"uid":149357,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"其實有無唸過人地覺得